### REGISTER A NEW COMPANY AND ADMIN ###

POST {{CondoSphere.API_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/register-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "My New Test Company",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@admin.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456"
}